{"tid":559563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「旅行奇遇」點幫個朋友走出陰影？","createTime":"2018-02-13T09:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T10:08:06.000Z","uid":32732,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81be6de02e174b1477054d2e2403b18384580862","tid":559563,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的⋯ 有個識左好耐既男朋友自從上個月去泰國後就一直自閉，連佢女朋友約佢都唔願出來，唔願見人，咁個個朋友都好擔心佢，終於約到佢出飲酒⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 我    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你搞咩，去完泰國返來就一直自閉？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔好問⋯ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：屌你！ 一世人兩兄弟你唔係唔講啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我⋯ 我去泰國時落吧玩，識左個女仔，之後仲去左爆房⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔通入到房，佢有棍？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：佢無棍⋯ 入到房仲口爆左佢一次，但當我插入時，佢唔需要用套己經好奇，入左後⋯ 我知道這是不是不是女人的陰道⋯ 我當時軟左⋯ 我立刻想拔返出來⋯ 但⋯ 但⋯ 佢好大力按住我⋯ 坐係我上面係咁郁⋯ 果一刻我覺得好似被人強姦咁⋯（呢個時候我朋友已經眼現淚光⋯）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 咁都唔關你事，你都係受害者⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：但我最嬲係，係我自己⋯ 之後我竟然有感覺！ 我高潮左！ 仲係個人妖入面射左2次！ 係2次！ 我仲⋯ 點見人⋯ <br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我除左把手上既藍妹給我朋友外， 我什麼都說不出。"},{"pid":"53748f50c3f116ee444c2657011a3bc25a3603a2","tid":559563,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c8ae923dbd32ff37c5a5c0a97457c7996665b4","tid":559563,"uid":114518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多，驗左身，驗左血先講。<br />\n一陣奶咗野就唔止一個陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\